formats.editor_svg:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
     width="800" height="340"
     viewBox="0 0 800 340">

  <style>
    <![CDATA[
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Bravura';
      src: url('/fonts/Bravura.woff2') format('woff2'),
           url('/fonts/Bravura.woff') format('woff');
      font-weight: normal;
      font-style: normal;
    }

    .canvas-content {
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    .canvas-note {
      font-size: 20px;
      fill: deepskyblue;
      font-weight: normal;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    .char {
      font-size: 20px;
      fill: deepskyblue;
      font-weight: normal;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
      cursor: text;
    }

    .char.cursor {
      fill: white;
      stroke: black;
      stroke-width: 2px;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    /* Semantic element styles */
    .note-char {
      font-size: 20px;
      fill: #1e90ff;
      font-weight: normal;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
      cursor: text;
    }

    .rest-char {
      font-size: 20px;
      fill: #808080;
      font-style: italic;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
      cursor: text;
    }

    .barline-char {
      font-size: 20px;
      fill: #8b008b;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
      cursor: text;
    }

    .dash-char {
      font-size: 20px;
      fill: #4682b4;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
      cursor: text;
    }

    .breath-char {
      font-size: 20px;
      fill: #ff6347;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
      cursor: text;
    }

    .lyrics-char {
      font-size: 18px;
      fill: #666666;
      font-style: italic;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
      cursor: text;
    }

    .text-char {
      font-size: 20px;
      fill: #333333;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
      cursor: text;
    }

    .unknown-char {
      font-size: 18px;
      fill: #999999;
      font-style: italic;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
      cursor: text;
    }

    .upper-char, .lower-char {
      font-size: 16px;
      fill: #ff4500;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
      cursor: text;
    }

    .octave-dot {
      fill: #ff0000;
    }

    .canvas-octave-upper {
      font-size: 12px;
      fill: red;
      font-weight: normal;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    .canvas-octave-lower {
      font-size: 12px;
      fill: red;
      font-weight: normal;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    .canvas-barline {
      font-size: 20px;
      fill: mediumorchid;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    /* Cursor CSS removed - handled by client-side JavaScript */

    .canvas-beat-arc {
      stroke: orange;
      stroke-width: 2;
      fill: none;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .canvas-selection {
      fill: rgba(65, 105, 225, 0.4);
      stroke: none;
    }

    .line-hitbox.highlighted {
        fill: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .canvas-placeholder {
      font-size: 18px;
      fill: gray;
      font-style: italic;
      font-weight: normal;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    .canvas-unknown {
      font-size: 16px;
      fill: gray;
      font-weight: normal;
      font-style: italic;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    .canvas-title {
      font-size: 30px;
      fill: black;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    .canvas-lyrics {
      font-size: 18px;
      fill: #666;
      font-style: italic;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    .canvas-text {
      font-size: 20px;
      fill: #333;
      font-weight: normal;
      font-family: monospace, 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    @keyframes blink {
      0%, 50% { opacity: 1; }
      51%, 100% { opacity: 0; }
    }

    /* Character replacement styles removed - handled in rendering logic */
    ]]>
  </style>
  <rect width="800" height="340" fill="#fafafa" stroke="#dddddd" stroke-width="1"/>
  <g class="canvas-content" transform="translate(20, 20)">
<g class="content-line">
    <rect class="line-hitbox" x="-20" y="-20" width="800" height="60" fill="transparent" />
    <g class="beat" data-beat-id="37dba3d8-40ce-4ecf-90bf-5253a6ae86ec" data-char-start="0">
      <g class="note" data-note-id="7591041d-0fa3-4e5a-a340-674717d71a64" data-octave="0">
        <text x="0.0" y="20.0" class="note-char" data-char-index="0" data-width="8.1">1</text>
      </g>
    </g>
    <g class="beat" data-beat-id="2a2f9878-5708-4ef3-b259-35c4b9411092" data-char-start="2">
      <g class="note" data-note-id="7095bb98-59e4-49d2-be02-e2f5196087d8" data-octave="0">
        <text x="13.8" y="20.0" class="note-char" data-char-index="2" data-width="12.2">2</text>
      </g>
    </g>
    <g class="beat" data-beat-id="394dbb1e-2a6c-4a61-aa34-ca9cb9f45d26" data-char-start="4">
      <g class="note" data-note-id="c4f0f4bd-464c-4293-b164-9259c658cbd2" data-octave="0">
        <text x="31.6" y="20.0" class="note-char" data-char-index="4" data-width="12.4">3</text>
      </g>
    </g>
    <g class="beat" data-beat-id="88d74e90-7d28-4dc4-a09e-a3be1fd6949c" data-char-start="6">
      <g class="note" data-note-id="58e4cf8b-62b0-4319-aed1-1a08505a58b2" data-octave="0">
        <text x="49.6" y="20.0" class="note-char" data-char-index="6" data-width="12.9">4</text>
      </g>
    </g>
    <g class="beat" data-beat-id="532e0679-7b20-4915-ac55-b5f96c27451c" data-char-start="8">
      <g class="note" data-note-id="1d23fce8-282e-4ae3-98b5-f8278ac31d45" data-octave="0">
        <text x="68.1" y="20.0" class="note-char" data-char-index="8" data-width="12.2">5</text>
      </g>
    </g>
</g>
  </g>
  <metadata id="coordinate-data">
    <![CDATA[
    {
      "elements": [
      ],
      "characterPositions": {
        "0": {"x": 0.0, "y": 20.0},

        "4": {"x": 31.6, "y": 20.0},
        "5": {"x": 43.9, "y": 20.0},
        "6": {"x": 49.6, "y": 20.0},
        "7": {"x": 62.5, "y": 20.0},
        "8": {"x": 68.1, "y": 20.0},
        "9": {"x": 80.3, "y": 20.0}
      }
    }
    ]]>
  </metadata>
</svg>
